---
import LucideIcon from './icons/LucideIcon';
---

<section id="testimonios" class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-white">
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<!-- Section Header -->
		<div class="text-center mb-16 lg:mb-20 testimonials-header">
			<div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-3 px-5 py-2.5 bg-[var(--color-surface-200)] rounded-full text-[var(--color-primary)] font-medium mb-10">
				<LucideIcon name="Quote" class="w-2.5 h-2.5 flex-shrink-0" client:load />
				<span class="text-sm">Testimonios</span>
			</div>
			<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-heading)] mb-6">
				Lo que dicen nuestros clientes
			</h2>
			<p class="text-xl text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
				La confianza de nuestras familias es nuestro mayor logro. Conoce las experiencias de quienes confían en nosotros para el cuidado de sus mascotas.
			</p>
		</div>

		<!-- Testimonials Grid -->
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
			<!-- Testimonial Card 1 -->
			<div class="bg-white rounded-[var(--radius-card)] p-8 shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-card-hover)] transition-all duration-300 border border-[var(--border-subtle-color)] testimonial-card">
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-1 mb-6">
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
				</div>
				<p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
					"Excelente atención profesional. El personal es muy amable y se nota que realmente se preocupan por el bienestar de los animales. Mi perro Max siempre recibe un trato excepcional y los diagnósticos son siempre precisos."
				</p>
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-primary)] to-[var(--color-primary-dark)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)]">
						MC
					</div>
					<div>
						<div class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text-heading)]">María Campos</div>
						<div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-tertiary)]">Dueña de Max</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Testimonial Card 2 -->
			<div class="bg-white rounded-[var(--radius-card)] p-8 shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-card-hover)] transition-all duration-300 border border-[var(--border-subtle-color)] testimonial-card">
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-1 mb-6">
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
				</div>
				<p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
					"Llevo a mi gata Luna aquí desde hace 2 años. Los veterinarios son muy profesionales, explican todo de manera clara y siempre están disponibles para resolver dudas. El seguimiento post-operatorio fue excelente."
				</p>
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-secondary)] to-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)]">
						JR
					</div>
					<div>
						<div class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text-heading)]">Juan Rodríguez</div>
						<div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-tertiary)]">Dueño de Luna</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Testimonial Card 3 -->
			<div class="bg-white rounded-[var(--radius-card)] p-8 shadow-[var(--shadow-card)] hover:shadow-[var(--shadow-card-hover)] transition-all duration-300 border border-[var(--border-subtle-color)] testimonial-card">
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-1 mb-6">
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
					<LucideIcon name="Star" class="w-5 h-5 fill-yellow-400 text-yellow-400" client:load />
				</div>
				<p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
					"El servicio de urgencias es excepcional. Cuando mi perro tuvo una emergencia, me atendieron de inmediato con total profesionalismo. El equipo médico es muy competente y las instalaciones están impecables. Altamente recomendado."
				</p>
				<div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-primary-light)] to-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)]">
						AS
					</div>
					<div>
						<div class="font-bold text-[var(--color-text-heading)]">Ana Sánchez</div>
						<div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-tertiary)]">Dueña de Rocky</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
